                        <td>
                        
                            <p><strong>My son died almost a decade and a half ago. I don&#39;t have nearly as many dreams about him now but when I do, as when I had many, many dreams of him...he never speaks. I can be virtually right next to him in a known location. He never talks. Is there an underlying meaning to this?</strong><br/>
DAVE, EL PASO, USA</p>

                        </td>
                    </tr>
